  "description": "<p>Hair wax sticks contain beeswax and glycerin. It can quickly shape at a touch, quickly shape, and last long. How to use it is very simple: 1. First, use a comb to soak some water and smooth it along the hair. 2. Open the lid and rotate the wax stick. 3. Repeat 3-4 times along the direction of the hair where you need to sort out the broken hair. And it can have a unique softness, form a delicate protective film on the hair, increase the gloss and smoothness of the hair, and make the style last longer.<br/></p><p><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/cd52db43-01b7-46be-9d37-1e11460dd50a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/be61a7dc-4f10-4755-9384-90e0947c859d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/eecf3c68-7c06-4f7b-8238-0016e87db889.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/cbd540b3-62fc-4188-b00a-23453a82eaa0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/d58edfa0-2f8a-4b07-a808-e5164eb38dba.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/cea0a65d-30e2-4a1b-b641-67156a73e341.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/></p>",
